description.en:
RakuCoin is a decentralized Meme coin owned by its community, with True Purpose and On going developments formed by a team of developers in Singapore with many up coming developments and goals ahead.

We are a long term project that is focusing on the developments of NFTs/Decentralized exchange/mobile apps/games/Technology etc....

Holders earn passive income with an Instant 2% rewards per transaction while just holding it in your wallet.
Holders will also benefit from our upcoming plans and on going developments developed for the team

$RAKUC will also be connecting with Animal home shelters for Charity events to give back not only to the community but also to the animals in need.
